28
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:14,701
So, our brain is doing right side activity
and that’s why our brain is like shriphala.

29
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:28,309
Sahasrara is actually is the
assemblage of these six chakras

30
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:38,144
and is a hollow space, on the sides
of it there are one thousand nadis.

31
