35
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:20,340
But the last one, ultimately becomes again
integrated and it is a crystal-clear flame.

36
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:27,194
All these seven lights
ultimately become crystal clear.

37
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:34,680
So, you have Sahasrara with one
thousand petals, as they called it,

